commit 0ee34467fed4cc2b170c0564e85d85870d93f586
Author: lyle <code@spengrah.xyz>
Date:   Tue Mar 3 10:34:37 2026 -0600

    task: add configurable ingestion profiles, agent mapping, and legacy migration (wave 8)
    
    Replace hardcoded ingestion directory assumptions with configurable
    profile-based target selection (PM6-R1), agent-to-profile mapping with
    defaultProfile fallback (PM6-R2), backward-compatible legacy config
    normalization with deprecation warnings (PM6-R3), safety defaults for
    excludes and extensions (PM6-R4), and per-profile/per-agent summary
    dimensions (PM6-R5). Includes 27 new tests, updated README with
    single-profile and multi-agent examples, and updated traceability map.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

